-- Seed data: personal insurance domain
-- All data is clean (no intentional DQ issues)
-- national_id format: 1 uppercase letter + 9 digits
-- gender: 'M' or 'F' only
-- product_type: 'life', 'health', or 'accident' only
-- policy status: 'active', 'lapsed', 'terminated' only
-- claim status: 'pending', 'approved', 'rejected', 'paid' only
-- expiry_date is always after effective_date
-- claim_amount does not exceed the policy's coverage_amount
-- All dates are in the past

